Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.57,0:01:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When random contexts{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.94,0:01:16.86,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ishi wo mochi tsunagareba{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.94,0:01:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Start to make sense on their own{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.91,0:01:23.29,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}toki no ito ga tsumugi naosareru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.91,0:01:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The threads of time are spun back together{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.62,0:01:28.83,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ore tachi to tomoni sekai kawari tsuzuketeru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.62,0:01:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The world keeps changing along with us{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.88,0:01:31.38,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(All of us) a-su, a-su{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.88,0:01:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(All of us) us, us{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.42,0:01:36.76,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(Dream save us us) a-su, All of us{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.42,0:01:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(Dream save us us) us, all of us{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.06,0:01:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}CP-0 who was out for Vegapunk's life...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.14,0:01:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...blocked all possible escape routes\Non Egghead.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.48,0:01:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Contain us to the island,\Nhunt us down, and take us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.11,0:01:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy's plan is effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.57,0:01:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.78,0:02:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There is one more ally on the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.24,0:02:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.54,0:02:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If that one takes our side now,\Nthey won't be able to stay where they are
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.00,0:02:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Government will hunt them down!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.12,0:02:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.58,0:02:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.84,0:02:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.92,0:02:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'm stuck in the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.21,0:02:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but could you save me-{\i1}Quasar{\i}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.14,0:02:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What a shameless cry for help!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.93,0:02:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Of course.\NI've been waiting for your order.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.48,0:02:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Turn Back My Father!\NBonney's Futile Wish!"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.49,0:02:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the Straw Hats' ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.91,0:02:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.91,0:02:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is why we didn't see their ship\Ndown there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.79,0:02:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.71,0:02:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.60,0:03:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll destroy it with one strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.56,0:03:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I finished the dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.19,0:03:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still time\Nso I might as well clean the deck, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.61,0:03:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what the alarm earlier was about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.21,0:03:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Tempest Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.55,0:03:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sky Slicer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.03,0:03:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.36,0:04:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.03,0:04:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that explosion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Who disrupted my sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.42,0:04:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.25,0:04:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, somebody was guarding the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.92,0:04:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Roronoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.01,0:04:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.81,0:04:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But my swordsmanship is the best in CP9.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.56,0:04:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.23,0:04:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What a tough guy you are.\NI'm flabbergasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.82,0:04:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I've trained my body, you damn gi-riff-raff!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.78,0:04:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Gi-riff-raff? I am a giraffe!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.74,0:04:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Gi-riff-raff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.41,0:04:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sky Slicer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.63,0:05:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Gi-riff-raff from Cipher Pol\Nthat I met some time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.09,0:05:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not Gi-riff-raff! I am a giraffe!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.97,0:05:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me handle this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're here for,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.56,0:05:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,but if you're trying to destroy our ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to slice you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.10,0:05:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.94,0:05:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Frontier Dome, activated.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.53,0:05:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Frontier Dome, activated.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.04,0:05:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Shaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.54,0:05:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The Frontier Dome has recovered,\Nbut CP-0 has already entered.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.92,0:05:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! It's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.01,0:05:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They're trying to destroy\Nthe Straw Hats' ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.85,0:05:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.89,0:05:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who must've been watching the ship\Nare fighting back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.44,0:06:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to back them up\Nor we'll lose our means of escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.15,0:06:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,See?! We need to fight after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.12,0:06:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta ambush CP-0!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.74,0:06:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down.\NI don't want you to get out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.46,0:06:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn Bonney! Where did she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.71,0:06:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad. We completely lost her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.43,0:06:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What was the alarm earlier about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.68,0:06:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a bad feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.86,0:06:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.82,0:06:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.61,0:06:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy! Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.49,0:06:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Jimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.04,0:06:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.63,0:07:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad that we met up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! There is a bunch of cool stuff here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.71,0:07:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.13,0:07:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we know!\NWe've been watching you on a monitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.80,0:07:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when you were in a fight\Nwith Cipher Pol.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.89,0:07:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that, we heard that\Nwe'd have Vegapunk aboard our ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.10,0:07:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.56,0:07:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We know what's up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.02,0:07:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's quickly get off this island\Nwith Vegapunk and the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.86,0:07:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! We're leaving already?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.57,0:07:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We just arrived on the island!\NLet's stay a little bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.83,0:07:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to as well! But this is\Nthe Government's island in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.91,0:07:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw Rob Lucci, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.63,0:07:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's going on outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.09,0:07:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Cipher Pol will get here soon,\Nso we can't waste any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.51,0:07:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.72,0:07:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see Bonney?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.85,0:08:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A female pirate with long hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.19,0:08:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that who you were with\Ndown at the robot?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.69,0:08:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,She's trying to kill Vegapunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.11,0:08:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.86,0:08:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.41,0:08:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of, where's Vegapunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.87,0:08:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I haven't seen him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.24,0:08:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Since when?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.08,0:08:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did he just go somewhere\Nwithout telling us? That old geezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.08,0:08:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee! Where did he go at a time like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.42,0:08:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope he hasn't been killed by Bonney.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.05,0:08:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.68,0:08:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Vegapunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.85,0:08:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Vegapunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.74,0:08:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop running!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:09:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Bonney!\NI don't have time for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But I want to talk to you!\NListen to me first!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.75,0:09:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.09,0:09:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Bonney!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.63,0:09:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.68,0:09:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What I wanna hear...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.68,0:09:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...is whether you can turn back my father\Nor not!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.64,0:09:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want a yes-or-no answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.35,0:09:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't... do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.73,0:09:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.81,0:09:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.33,0:09:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no choice but to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.25,0:09:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But there is a reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.05,0:09:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.55,0:09:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.98,0:10:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Bonney.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.26,0:10:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it won't accept her,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.01,0:10:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,she came in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.18,0:10:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She is undeniably human.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.98,0:10:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.48,0:10:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.65,0:10:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...this is a great first step toward peace\Nfor the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.95,0:11:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Vegapunk, the director of MADS,\Nthe Laboratory for Peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.50,0:11:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.09,0:11:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I broke a bone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.97,0:11:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Bonney.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.01,0:11:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.89,0:11:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.14,0:11:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?!\NI have to get the medical team!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.44,0:11:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Bonney got hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.74,0:11:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Distorted Future!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.24,0:11:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Vegapunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.08,0:11:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.75,0:11:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I was fooled!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.51,0:12:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop running!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.30,0:12:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't, Bonney!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.43,0:12:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you kill me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.76,0:12:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Age Skewer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.63,0:12:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't run anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.63,0:12:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.50,0:12:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,These glittering objects\Nare the years I lost, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.30,0:12:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you turn me\Ninto a helpless child?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.64,0:12:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me back the shining years of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.89,0:12:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.77,0:12:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My powers don't affect\Nliving things permanently.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.52,0:13:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You said there was a reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.49,0:13:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.66,0:13:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Why... did you kill my father?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.66,0:13:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I tell you, Bonney...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.04,0:13:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,it'll... only hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.84,0:13:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.59,0:13:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I made a promise with Kuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:35.89,On Top,sign,0,0,0,,RED PORT
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.85,0:13:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuma started climbing the Red Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.02,0:13:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way he can get to the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I promised him that\NI would never tell you the reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.42,0:14:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You had a reason to kill my father,\Nbut you can't say it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.67,0:14:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I'm stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.47,0:14:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.13,0:14:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think... you're stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.68,0:14:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.60,0:14:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The decision to give up his humanity...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.77,0:14:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...was his own, not anyone else's!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.73,0:14:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.82,0:14:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no way he'd leave me behind\Nand try to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.20,0:14:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You killed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.03,0:14:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It was hard for me, too!\NI don't even want to remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.93,0:14:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuma is a respectable man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.93,0:14:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm proud to call him my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:15:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I really like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.23,0:15:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So please understand, Bonney!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.31,0:15:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.32,0:15:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No, tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.40,0:15:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I be convinced\Nby such a self-serving excuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.49,0:15:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're abusing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.25,0:15:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.47,0:15:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.81,0:15:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.56,0:15:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's nothing. Wait, Bonney!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.02,0:15:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It has nothing to do with Kuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.44,0:15:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Hey, don't go there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.66,0:15:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.46,0:16:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oiled Shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.20,0:16:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Bonney!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.31,0:17:07.19,On Top,sign,0,0,0,,A CERTAIN SEA AREA, NEW WORLD
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.87,0:17:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The fish was exceptionally big!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.58,0:17:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's apparently not a normal sea area.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.09,0:17:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.43,0:17:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that an island?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.27,0:17:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Kid, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.81,0:17:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We're arriving at an island.\NShould we make landfall?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.60,0:17:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you asking that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.69,0:17:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no island\Nwe'd be hesitant to land on now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.36,0:17:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.29,0:18:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I assume that island\Nis the home of the Giants!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.71,0:18:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Elbaph!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.29,0:18:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Elbaph...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.46,0:18:15.55,On Top,sign,0,0,0,,NAVAL BRANCH G-14
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.72,0:18:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break, Vice Admiral Garp!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.84,0:18:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We're planning to leave for Egghead soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.64,0:18:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't take any of my troops away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.56,0:18:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so uptight, Doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.19,0:18:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you laughing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.02,0:18:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, if you're gonna attack an island\Noccupied by an Emperor of the Sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.11,0:18:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,did you get permission...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.90,0:18:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...from the brass?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.86,0:18:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What? Why do I need it?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.16,0:18:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been in the Navy for decades\Nand you don't know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.96,0:18:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.62,0:18:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm already here.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.29,0:18:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,"Here"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.34,0:18:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.51,0:18:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Koby-{\i1}senpai{\i}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.18,0:19:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Helmeppo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.09,0:19:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.56,0:19:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.93,0:19:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a pirate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.02,0:19:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they calling Helmeppo\Nto kill him alone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.44,0:19:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No! That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.86,0:19:23.20,On Top,sign,0,0,0,,JUSTICE
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.03,0:19:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Helmeppo! There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Vice Admiral Garp!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.20,0:19:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.08,0:19:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Koby... He got caught by Blackbeard...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.88,0:19:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.63,0:19:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop crying! How pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.39,0:19:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Vice Admiral Garp!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.35,0:19:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.06,0:19:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...get on board!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.14,0:19:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll set out for\Nthe Pirate Island of Beehive...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.02,0:19:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...to beat the hell out of the pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.48,0:20:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and rescue...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.15,0:20:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...Captain Koby!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.57,0:20:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Vice Admiral Garp!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.04,0:20:21.17,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}doredake hashitte kita noka{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.04,0:20:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How far I have run{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:28.47,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}wakaranai mama kizuato kazoeta{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Without knowing it, I counted scars{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.93,0:20:35.90,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}zutto atama no naka ni aru takara no chizu{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.93,0:20:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A treasure map in my head all along{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:42.40,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mirai wo sagashi tsuzuketeru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still looking for the future{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.45,0:20:49.12,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hontou no yakusoku wa{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.45,0:20:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The real promise{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:56.29,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mune no oku no motto oku ni aru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lies much deeper in my heart{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.33,0:21:05.43,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}dare mo mina oitsukenai yume{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.33,0:21:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A dream that no one can catch up with{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.47,0:21:11.14,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitotsu dakishimete{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.47,0:21:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's all I hold on to{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.18,0:21:18.23,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}taiyou no youni warau anata e{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.18,0:21:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To you who smiles like the sun{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.27,0:21:25.15,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ano hi to onaji uta wo utau yo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.27,0:21:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll sing the same song as that day{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:32.20,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}otona ni nattemo wasuretakunai{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This wish I don't want to forget even when I grow up{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.24,0:21:39.67,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kono negai ga todoku made{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.24,0:21:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Until it reaches you{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.38,0:21:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Dive into the Sea of Information!\NThe Punk Records Library!"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.72,0:21:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, I'm Lilith, one of the Satellites of\NDr. Vegapunk, the genius scientist!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.39,0:21:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Edison, also Vegapunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.27,0:22:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Today we'll introduce this one!\NEustass "Captain" Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.44,0:22:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He is the captain of the Kid Pirates\Nand a pirate from the Worst Generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.11,0:22:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,His bounty is the same as Straw Hat,\N3 billion berries.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.74,0:22:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He uses the Magnet-Magnet Fruit power
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.37,0:22:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,which enables him to manipulate metal\Nwith magnetic forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.70,0:22:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He was born on January 10th\Nand likes cabbage rolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.79,0:22:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Just for the record,\Nhis least favorite food is curry udon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.38,0:22:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The belligerent Kid Pirates quickly\Ndistinguished themselves even in the New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.97,0:22:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,They boldly challenged the Emperors of the Sea,\Nthe Red-Hair Pirates and the Big Mom Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.01,0:22:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when he allied with Basil Hawkins\Nand Scratchmen Apoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.85,0:22:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But he was betrayed by them, captured by Kaido,\Nand imprisoned at the Land of Wano.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.23,0:22:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He escaped, but tried to rescue Killer,\Nhis childhood friend and partner,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.57,0:22:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,so he ended up being tortured and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.36,0:22:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,After he somehow managed to free himself,\Nhe and Trafalgar Law confronted Big Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.87,0:22:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And after a great struggle,\Nthey finally defeated the Emperor of the Sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.58,0:23:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me help you...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.75,0:23:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...get to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.34,0:23:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kid now has a bounty on his head\Nequal to that of Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.63,0:23:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to see his future rampages!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.26,0:23:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.88,0:23:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you've seen it,\Ndonate to our research fund!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.43,0:23:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,See you next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.52,0:23:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}CP-0 descends on the Labophase\Nwith overwhelming force!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.65,0:23:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Seraphim unleash laser beams\Nwithout mercy!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.69,0:23:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Will that flash of light accomplish\Nthe assassination of Vegapunk?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.95,0:23:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The lab is on the verge of destruction.\NIs it all over for the Straw Hats?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.74,0:23:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.29,0:23:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"A Desperate Situation!\NThe Seraphim's All-out Attack!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.62,0:23:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
